      <title>为什么匈牙利选举可能会因罗姆人的选票而左右摇摆</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/07/world/europe/hungary-roma-orban-election-education.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总理维克托·欧尔班影响罗姆少数民族的政策使这些选民在即将举行的议会选举中发挥作用。在一场激烈的比赛中，他们可以发挥重要作用。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/07/world/europe/hungary-roma-orban-election-education.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 Apr 2026 07:00:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿耳忒弥斯二号宇航员在完成历史性的绕月之旅后启程回家</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/06/science/space/nasa-artemis-moon-flyby.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国宇航局月球飞越之旅使四名宇航员比任何人类都离地球更远。他们目睹了日食，并受到特朗普总统的称赞。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/06/science/space/nasa-artemis-moon-flyby.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 Apr 2026 05:05:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>万斯将访问匈牙利，在选举前提振欧尔班</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/07/world/europe/vance-hungary-orban-fidesz-election.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国副总统万斯 (JD Vance) 的定期访问表明，俄罗斯并不是唯一一个为匈牙利领导人维克托·欧尔班 (Viktor Orban) 的胜利而投资的国家。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/07/world/europe/vance-hungary-orban-fidesz-election.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 Apr 2026 04:01:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴黎地下墓穴的修复能否为这座城市的死者带来新的生命？</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/07/world/europe/paris-catacombs-renovation.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[几个世纪以来，大约六百万人的尸骨被埋在城市地下的墓穴中。策展人正在努力保护隧道并使之现代化，同时保持怪异的氛围。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/07/world/europe/paris-catacombs-renovation.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 Apr 2026 04:01:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普表示伊朗的提议不足以阻止对桥梁和发电厂的袭击</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/06/us/politics/trump-iran-cease-fire-proposal.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特朗普总统告诉伊朗，必须在晚上 8 点之前开放霍尔木兹海峡。周二或面临后果，尽管他已经推迟了之前的最后期限。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/06/us/politics/trump-iran-cease-fire-proposal.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 Apr 2026 02:53:31 GMT</pubDate>
